    "owner": "SSD Team",
    "description": "Threat model for SecureShop, an online store web application. Customers register, log in, browse a catalogue, and check out. Stores credentials, PII, and order history; payment is delegated to an external gateway.",
    "id": 0
  },
  "detail": {
